Type: Package
Package: topicdoc
Title: Topic-specific diagnostics for LDA and CTM topic models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Doug",
           family = "Friedman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "doug.nhp@gmail.com")
Description: Calculates topic-specific diagnostics (e.g. mean token length, exclusivity) for 
    Latent Dirichelet Allocation and Correlated Topic Models fit using the topicmodels package.
    These diagnostics originate from Boyd-Graber et al. (2014, ISBN:9781466504080), 
    Mimno et al. (2011, ISBN:9781937284114), and Bischof et al. (2014) <arXiv:1206.4631v1>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/doug-friedman/topicdoc
BugReports: https://github.com/doug-friedman/topicdoc/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    slam,
    topicmodels
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
VignetteBuilder: 
    knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
